# Implementation Plan - 榊原税理士事務所 (Sakakibara Tax Office) Website

## Goal Description
Create a professional, responsive top page for "榊原税理士事務所" (Sakakibara Tax Accountant Office). The design must reflect a Japanese corporate aesthetic (trustworthy, clean, high-quality) using the specified color palette.

## Specifications
- **Main Color**: #1F2A44 (Deep Navy)
- **Sub Color**: #BDAA4B (Gold)
- **Base Color**: #F4F4F2 (Warm Gray)
- **Target**: Top page (First View + basic corporate sections) aka "Canvas".
- **Tech Stack**: HTML5, CSS3 (Vanilla, BEM methodology).

